data.description: 3BR 2BA. 1.5 STORY. ~1800 SQFT. SPACIOUS 1.53 ACRE LOT. BEAUTIFUL FLOORS. NEW HVAC. NEW GUTTERS  Welcome home to this charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom bungalow nestled on a spacious 1.5-acre lot. Boasting approximately 1800 square feet spread across 1.5 stories, this residence seamlessly blends unique character with modern conveniences. The master bedroom is a true retreat, featuring a wood-burning fireplace that adds a touch of warmth and elegance. Imagine cozy evenings by the fire in the comfort of your own bedroom. The well-designed kitchen is a culinary delight, offering an abundance of cabinet and countertop space, along with a convenient kitchen island. Whether you're entertaining guests or preparing family meals, this kitchen is both stylish and functional. As you explore the home, you'll be captivated by the beautiful floors that grace each room. Natural light pours in through numerous windows, creating a bright and inviting atmosphere throughout. The office/study provides a dedicated space for work or leisure, adding to the home's versatility. Step outside to the expansive 1.5-acre lot, offering a picturesque setting for outdoor activities and relaxation. Conveniently located just minutes from downtown Greenville and the Travelers Rest/Furman area, this home provides the perfect balance of tranquility and access to the vibrant city life. Don't miss the opportunity to call this unique property your own – a harmonious blend of comfort, style, and convenience in an ideal location. Your dream home awaits!
